Soundboard recording from the famous Rockpalast concert. Taken from the original
silver pressed bootleg "Sultans of Swing - Live in Germany". Great concert including
very nice versions of Single handed sailor and Follow me home. Notice that they
played Sultans of Swing twice because Mark was very unhappy with the way he
played it the first time: "Alright now, let's do this Sultans and do it properly.....
" Very rare that this happens! The atmosphere is terrific on this concert,
a must to have! Complete and uncut show
